# Generated Proxy Files (avoid polluting the source repo with example outputs)
DllProxyGenerator/*.def
DllProxyGenerator/*.asm
DllProxyGenerator/CMakeLists.txt
# Only ignore generated .cpp files, not the source main.cpp
DllProxyGenerator/*.cpp
!DllProxyGenerator/main.cpp